metadata.name: Light x Darkness [1]
metadata.description: Sculpted by hand and from scratch in ZBrush with no premade models used, this exploration into perfection and turmoil allowed me to learn and experiment with Houdini and its particle simulation system. This is the start of a whole new direction and avenue of expression being my first animation and my first 3d based NFT. I hope you'll join me on this journey which will be composed of 4 1/1 pieces.
